snippet: China’s state media confirmed that two people, from the provinces of Anhui and Jiangsu in the eastern part of the country, had died Tuesday from the H7N9 virus.
lead_paragraph: China’s state media confirmed that two people, from the provinces of Anhui and Jiangsu in the eastern part of the country, had died Tuesday from the H7N9 virus.

headline.main: China Reports 2 More Deaths From Bird Flu
